<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.3.1">
<l>ēttu kiṉṟōm nātta ḻumpa virāmaṉ tirunāmam</l>
<l>cōttam nampī cukki rīvā yummait toḻukiṉṟōm</l>
<l>vārttai pēcīr emmai yuṅkaḷ vāṉa ramkollāmē</l>
<l>kūttar pōla vāṭu kiṉṟōm kuḻama ṇitūramē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We are praising Rāma’s divine name until our tongues ache;</l>
<l>“Praises, Prince! Sugrīva! We revere you.</l>
<l>Declare [your] promise of your monkeys not killing us.”</l>
<l>Like performers, we are dancing to the kuḻamaṇitūram.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
